# Plan: musl/Alpine Linux Binary Support

**Issue:** https://github.com/getsentry/cli/issues/754

## Summary

Add `sentry-linux-x64-musl` and `sentry-linux-arm64-musl` native binaries so Alpine Linux and other musl-based systems can use the curl installer and self-upgrade. Bun natively supports `bun-linux-x64-musl` and `bun-linux-arm64-musl` compile targets, making this straightforward.

